text: Seth Kwame Dzokoto is a Ghanaian comedian, actor and politician. He is the host to the Edziban show on TV3; which explores Ghanaian food joints and cuisines. ==Politics== He contested on the tickets of National Democratic Congress during the 2016 Ghanaian general elections in the Tarkwa-Nsuaem constituency but lost to Mireku Duker of the New Patriotic Party. ==Filmography== *Efiewura == References == Category:Living people Category:Ghanaian comedians Category:Ghanaian politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
